---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn about Hustle Teacher — your guide to making money online through practical guides, tools, and proven digital strategies."
	pubDate={new Date('January 01 2024')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2 class="heading-gold text-4xl mb-6 mt-12 text-center reveal">My Story</h2>
	
	<div class="divider reveal">
	  <div class="divider-line"></div>
	  <div class="divider-coin">$</div>
	  <div class="divider-line"></div>
	</div>

	<p class="prose-italic text-xl text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 reveal">
		Hi, I'm <strong>Parth</strong>, the founder of Hustle Teacher. I started this platform with one simple mission: to demystify the process of making money online and empower everyday people to build their own digital income streams. 
	</p>

	<div class="stats-bar reveal rounded-2xl mb-12 mt-8">
		<div class="stats-item">
			<span class="stats-val">50+</span>
			<span class="stats-label">Guides</span>
		</div>
		<div class="stats-item">
			<span class="stats-val">10k</span>
			<span class="stats-label">Readers</span>
		</div>
		<div class="stats-item">
			<span class="stats-val">24/7</span>
			<span class="stats-label">Hustle</span>
		</div>
	</div>

	<p class="prose-italic text-lg mb-6 reveal">
		The internet is full of noise—get-rich-quick schemes, overpriced courses, and confusing jargon. I created Hustle Teacher to cut through that noise. My philosophy is straightforward: <strong class="text-gold">Learn → Start → Earn</strong>. We focus on proven, actionable strategies that actually work in today's digital economy.
	</p>

	<p class="prose-italic text-lg mb-6 reveal">
		Whether you're a student looking for a side gig, a professional wanting to transition into freelancing, or an aspiring entrepreneur ready to launch a scalable online business, I've designed this space for you. I spend countless hours researching and testing the methods we recommend, so you don't have to guess what works.
	</p>

	<p class="prose-italic text-lg mb-12 reveal">
		From detailed blueprints on dropshipping and YouTube automation to carefully curated free tools and premium digital products, our goal is to provide everything you need under one roof. I believe that with the right guidance and a bit of hustle, financial independence is within everyone's reach. Let's start building your empire today.
	</p>

	<div class="flex justify-center reveal mb-12">
		<a href="/start-here/" class="btn-gold">Start Your Journey</a>
	</div>
</Layout>
